### Create Normal Exam
POST http://localhost:3000/exams
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "normal",
  "subject": "Mathematics",
  "maxScore": 100,
  "scoreDistributions": [
    { "section_name": "Section A", "allocated_score": 40 },
    { "section_name": "Section B", "allocated_score": 60 }
  ],
  "scoreMappings": [
    { "min_score": 0, "max_score": 39, "status": "Fail" },
    { "min_score": 40, "max_score": 100, "status": "Pass" }
  ]
}

### Create Continuous Exam
POST http://localhost:3000/exams
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "continuous",
  "subject": "Science",
  "maxScore": 50
}

### Get All Exams
GET http://localhost:3000/exams

### Create Result
POST http://localhost:3000/results
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "examId": 1,
  "studentId": "STD001",
  "obtainedScore": 85,
  "metadata": { "section_a": 35, "section_b": 50 }
}

### Get All Results
GET http://localhost:3000/results
